  "title": "Admin / Reservations Executive (up to $3,000 base | F&B Group)",
  "description": "<h3>Responsibilities</h3><ul><li><p>Manage and coordinate daily reservations across phone, WhatsApp, email, and online platforms</p></li><li><p>Maintain accurate reservation records, guest profiles, and seating plans</p></li><li><p>Support outlet operations with basic administrative duties (reports, filing, data updates)</p></li><li><p>Handle guest enquiries professionally and ensure timely follow-ups</p></li><li><p>Liaise with outlet teams to ensure smooth service flow and guest experience</p></li><li><p>Assist with special requests, events, and group bookings when required</p></li></ul><h3>Requirements</h3><ul><li><p>Prior experience in F&B, hospitality, reservations, or admin support preferred</p></li><li><p>Comfortable handling multiple communication channels in a fast-paced environment</p></li><li><p>Strong attention to detail and organisational skills</p></li><li><p>Customer-focused, well-spoken, and able to manage priorities effectively</p></li></ul><p>Tyson Jay Management Pte Ltd | EA License No.: 24C2479</p><p>Ivan Lim | EA Personnel No.: R1109856</p>",
